      "title": "Klein 9B DISTILLED — scene + character ref",
      "properties": {},
      "widgets_values": [
        "## FLUX.2 Klein 9B **DISTILLED** — **сцена + референс + LoRA**\n\n**ComfyUI 0.9+** + **ComfyUI-GGUF** + **`ReferenceLatent`**\n\n### Модели\n| Файл | Папка |\n|------|--------|\n| `flux2-klein-9b-uncensored-q8_0.gguf` | `text_encoders/` |\n| **`flux-2-klein-9b-fp8.safetensors`** | `diffusion_models/` |\n| `flux2-vae.safetensors` | `vae/` |\n| **LoRA под Klein 9B** | `loras/` |\n\n### LoRA\n- Только LoRA **для FLUX.2 Klein 9B**\n- При конфликте с референсом снизьте **strength** (0.5–0.7)\n\n### Marinara\n- API: `flux2-klein-9b-scene-reference.api.json`\n- `%prompt%`, `%reference_image_name%`, `%width%`, `%height%`, `%seed%`\n\n### Параметры DISTILLED\n- **Steps:** 4 · **CFG:** 1 · **Sampler:** euler / simple\n\nКачество → `flux2-klein-9b-base-scene-reference.json` (BASE, 28 steps)\n"
      ],
      "color": "#432",
      "bgcolor": "#000"
    },
